    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222960/extras/e755c8ccaf7c1e1fc9132ec028cb769f.avif?t=1770712800\" width=600 height=250 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《悠久之树》是一款描述跨越神代与现代旅程的回合制战斗角色扮演游戏。恢弘的诗篇，未知的挑战，提塔尔耶拉大陆等您亲临探索。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【世界观巨献】</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>▽幻想世界的恢弘诗篇</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222960/extras/9ed405b4ce627b7c350934d5394169f7.avif?t=1770712800\" width=600 height=250 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >大陆「提塔尔耶拉」，是一片神代文明与现代文明交融的土地，神代神明留下的遗迹里埋藏着诸多珍贵的遗产。现代人探索神代遗迹，通过研究遗迹中的遗物使得文明获得了飞速的发展。那些以发掘遗迹为生的人们，被统称为“探求者”。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222960/extras/e82469dacb152cdccd4f15e4fd2d7461.avif?t=1770712800\" width=600 height=274 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与神秘人偶阿尔泰米西娅的偶然相遇，使身为普通探求者的你，卷入了大陆「提塔尔耶拉」跨越时代的纷争中。你的冒险，将决定这个世界未来的走向。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【沉浸式体验】</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>▽</strong>剧情中巧用各类图像素材，呈现出了丰富多彩的视觉效果。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >展现出紧张感十足的战斗场景，富有动感栩栩如生，仿佛是一部精美的动画番剧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222960/extras/eb296d4c3b77eecf424a285b2e37116b.poster.avif?t=1770712800\" width=600 height=328 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222960/extras/eb296d4c3b77eecf424a285b2e37116b.webm?t=1770712800\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222960/extras/eb296d4c3b77eecf424a285b2e37116b.mp4?t=1770712800\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>▽在</strong>华丽而独特的美术风格表现下，丰富各异性格鲜明的角色，守护你的冒险！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222960/extras/f440d85e1525f962ff1cf64b1def4eb2.avif?t=1770712800\" width=600 height=332 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>▽使用强大的调律爆发决定战斗的胜负</strong>！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222960/extras/bdc3c873cc6bb699b468a0223d715ac5.poster.avif?t=1770712800\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222960/extras/bdc3c873cc6bb699b468a0223d715ac5.webm?t=1770712800\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222960/extras/bdc3c873cc6bb699b468a0223d715ac5.mp4?t=1770712800\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>▽召唤强大的虚数体发动虚数降临</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222960/extras/15bfab0c68ec8ab31c89f78bf99b74c8.poster.avif?t=1770712800\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222960/extras/15bfab0c68ec8ab31c89f78bf99b74c8.webm?t=1770712800\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222960/extras/15bfab0c68ec8ab31c89f78bf99b74c8.mp4?t=1770712800\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>▽与形色各异的伙伴们一起超越极限</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222960/extras/e79a3e38c096d122f6a3fe2fb269374b.avif?t=1770712800\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222960/extras_big/e79a3e38c096d122f6a3fe2fb269374b.avif?t=1770712800 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>▽极具策略性的装备搭配</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222960/extras/fdb9cac94af85a434098f14b5d03c20c.avif?t=1770712800\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222960/extras_big/fdb9cac94af85a434098f14b5d03c20c.avif?t=1770712800 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【精美立绘】</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>▽冒险的同时休憩一刻</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222960/extras/ea97b7160ecf3872a566c5d6458199f8.avif?t=1770712800\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222960/extras_big/ea97b7160ecf3872a566c5d6458199f8.avif?t=1770712800 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222960/extras/0cac2cc6ac3987d79788518ecfd3813d.avif?t=1770712800\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222960/extras_big/0cac2cc6ac3987d79788518ecfd3813d.avif?t=1770712800 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【游戏特色】</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >· 超经典回合制战斗，打造属于你的强力队伍！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >· 主线剧情开启至第十一章，独特视觉小说式剧情演出加深沉浸冒险！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >· 精美角色、酷炫机神立绘带来独特绮美浪漫！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >· 丰厚新手入门奖励加速养成，迅速展开精彩冒险！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
